#: src/nd-window.ui:28
msgid "No Wi‑Fi P2P Adapter Found"
msgstr "Cap d'adaptator Wi-Fi P2P pas trobat"

#: src/nd-window.ui:29
msgid ""
"No usable wireless adapters were found. Please verify that Wi‑Fi is enabled "
"and Wi‑Fi P2P operations are available in both NetworkManager and "
"wpa_supplicant."
msgstr ""
"Cap d’adaptador sens fial pas trobat. Mercés de verificar que lo Wi-Fi es "
"activat e que las operacions Wi-Fi P2P son disponiblas dins NetworkManager e "
"wpa_supplicant."

